data.description: Large home on a private well ready for animals! Front covered porch sets off the country charm of this large home with room to expand! 360views! Lake and mountain views from the front, mountain views in the back. Main floor has living and family room flows into formal dining room and open kitchen . Enjoy morning coffee in the breakfast / sunroom just off the kitchen. Upper level has split bedroom floor plan with large master, en suite and walk in closet; three other bedroom and full bath. Basement, with outside own exterior access, is unfinished. Sitting on 2 acres property with a nice sized barn for to keep your animals out of the weather this winter! Come check out this home! Directions Left on McClellan, left at top of hill onto Grebe, right onto Pickering, right onto Hummingbird. There is a bus stop at the mailboxes for all the schools.
